&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Masterpieces are speaking for themselves.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intricate inaugural posts are tiresome.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thus, I have two factors perfectly intertwining for just displaying a crumb of &lt;em&gt;mathematical beauty&lt;/em&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;!-- regarding the illustrious constants: --&gt;
&lt;!-- # this is a perfect context for displaying
#They are a perfect context for an inaugural post which usually has few words.
#Thus, it is worthy to release our launching post with a crumb of _mathematical beauty_ : --&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;$$e^{i\pi} + 1 = 0.$$&lt;/p&gt;

